    [
      [
        "NO"
      ],
      [
        "[Paul], calm down! It’s just a stupid game,"
      ],
      [
        "there’s no need to get like that!"
      ],
      [
        "What did you just say?"
      ],
      [
        "[He] turns to me and glares at me."
      ],
      [
        "I had never seen [him] with this amount of rage in [his] eyes."
      ],
      [
        "[He] then takes hurried steps towards me."
      ],
      [
        "I try to open a drawer where I have a fake taser just to scare [him] off,"
      ],
      [
        "but [He] manages to grab my wrist and punches me in my nose. "
      ],
      [
        "I grab my face as I feel tears fall down."
      ],
      [
        "YOU NEVER TAKE SHIT SERIOUSLY, DO YOU?"
      ],
      [
        "Another punch makes me fall down from my chair,"
      ],
      [
        "I fall harshly on my hurt leg and I scream in pain. "
      ],
      [
        "[Paul] approaches me and begins to kick me on my side. "
      ],
      [
        "YOU’RE NOT BETTER THAN ME."
      ],
      [
        "YOU WILL NEVER BE."
      ],
      [
        "I WON’T CALM DOWN JUST BECAUSE YOU ASKED ME."
      ],
      [
        "KNOW YOUR PLACE."
      ],
      [
        "As I lay there, defenseless, I remember how [he] had come in here earlier promising me that [he]"
      ],
      [
        "would never hurt me again."
      ],
      [
        "Liar. "
      ],
      [
        "This attitude wouldn't change from one day to another, change takes time."
      ],
      [
        "But I was too naive to realize that… I was too blinded by my one-sided love."
      ],
      [
        "My body hurts, but my heart aches with the hurt of the betrayal of somebody who I thought would really care about me."
      ],
      [
        "Now I know… that I need to be alert, that I need to get away at the first sign of disrespect and abuse."
      ],
      [
        "Because violence comes so easily to someone who sees you beneath them,"
      ],
      [
        "and violence will always escalate one step further. "
      ],
      [
        "Healthy relationships are made with love and respect. Not… this..."
      ],
      [
        "But all this knowledge ends up useless anyways, as I feel [Paul]’s feet kick me on the head again and again."
      ],
      [
        "I look out the window and think “What will Helpie do when he sees me like this?”."
      ],
      [
        "That was the last thing on my mind, as it all fades to black… "
      ]
    ],
